PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of HARRY THOMAS DOYLE of Lower Coverdale, New Brunswick, as a member of the National Capital Commission to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective August 22, 2003, in the place of Dana B.
